    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. It's a great find for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
