    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65B40 platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 features individual throttle bodies and a cross-bank exhaust manifold, delivering peak torque through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure longevity. The chassis benefits from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M Variable Differential Lock that remains tight and responsive. Free of subframe cracks and exhibiting consistent VANOS timing, this vehicle represents a purist-spec driver\u2019s car with sorted internals and robust performance metrics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. Reliable performance. Inspect in person.",
